{"id":"5d9fee20ceafca31bd2bfe7c1a9ed404a68818ad","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/1228279","title":"能否把逻辑跟 AI 说清楚，让它先不要写实际代码(pyside6 界面)。而是先用最简单的 html 把页面/按钮布局和伪数据把图表/折线图等递进的逻辑关系表达出来？ 经过审核，觉得可以再用代码实施呢？","site_name":"Info Flow","source":"V2EX (创意工作者社区)","byline":"blackantt","excerpt":"程序员 - @blackantt - 类似于逻辑效果图吧，可以吗？","content_html":"<DIV class=\"page\" id=\"readability-page-1\"><div id=\"Main\">\n                \n                \n<div><p>类似于逻辑效果图吧，可以吗？</p></div>\n\n<!-- SOL tip topic -->\n\n\n\n\n\n<div>\n    <div><P><a href=\"/tag/逻辑\"><li></li> 逻辑</a><a href=\"/tag/HTML\"><li></li> HTML</a><a href=\"/tag/界面\"><li></li> 界面</a></P><p><span>8 replies &#160;<strong>•</strong> &#160;2026-07-19 08:53:10 +08:00</span>\n    </p></div>\n    \n\n    \n        \n        \n    \n    \n\n    \n        \n        <div id=\"r_17879904\">\n        \n        <table>\n            <tr>\n                <td><img src=\"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/479c/3b11/41753_normal.png?m=1756537907\" alt=\"Cu635\" data-uid=\"41753\"></td>\n                <td></td>\n                <td><p><span>2</span></p>\n                    \n                    <strong><a href=\"/member/Cu635\">Cu635</a></strong> &#160; &#160; &#160;<span title=\"2026-07-19 00:01:58 +08:00\">22h 29m ago</span> \n                    \n                    <p>这个步骤叫确认细化需求，一般是用另一个大模型，讨论、确认、调整、确认，生成详细需求描述，再把描述输入给写代码的大模型生成代码。</p>\n                </td>\n            </tr>\n        </table>\n        </div>\n    \n    \n\n    \n        \n        <div id=\"r_17879908\">\n        \n        <table>\n            <tr>\n                <td><img src=\"https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/315462ba2040d4466fcb89b93908ef35?s=48&d=retro\" alt=\"gorvey\" data-uid=\"532463\"></td>\n                <td></td>\n                <td><p><span>3</span></p>\n                    \n                    <strong><a href=\"/member/gorvey\">gorvey</a></strong> &#160; &#160; &#160;<span title=\"2026-07-19 00:06:21 +08:00\">22h 25m ago</span> \n                    \n      